### Franchises API — ejemplos de uso
### Compatible con el HTTP Client de IntelliJ y la extensión REST Client de VS Code.
### Ejecuta las peticiones en orden: las variables se rellenan desde las respuestas.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Crear franquicia
# @name createFranchise
POST {{host}}/api/v1/franchises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Franquicia Norte"
}

> {% client.global.set("franchiseId", response.body.id); %}

### 2. Agregar sucursal
# @name addBranch
POST {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sucursal Centro"
}

> {% client.global.set("branchId", response.body.id); %}

### 3. Agregar producto
# @name addProduct
POST {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto A",
  "stock": 50
}

> {% client.global.set("productId", response.body.id); %}

### 4. Agregar un segundo producto (mayor stock)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto B",
  "stock": 120
}

### 5. Modificar stock
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products/{{productId}}/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stock": 200
}

### 6. Producto con más stock por sucursal
GET {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/top-stock-products

### 7. Renombrar franquicia
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Franquicia Norte Renombrada"
}

### 8. Renombrar sucursal
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sucursal Centro Renombrada"
}

### 9. Renombrar producto
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products/{{productId}}/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto A Renombrado"
}

### 10. Eliminar producto
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products/{{productId}}

### --- Casos de error ---

### Stock negativo -> 400
POST {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/{{franchiseId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Inválido",
  "stock": -5
}

### Franquicia inexistente -> 404
GET {{host}}/api/v1/franchises/inexistente/branches/top-stock-products
